.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:62:+-- score-candidate.cjs       # Lane entrypoint: dynamic 5-dimension scorer
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:66:+-- trade-off-detector.cjs    # Library: cross-dimension regression detection
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:67:+-- benchmark-stability.cjs   # Library: score variance + weight advisory
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:68:+-- check-mirror-drift.cjs    # CLI: canonical-to-mirror drift report
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:79:| `score-candidate.cjs` | Lane entrypoint. Reads candidate (and optional baseline), spawns `generate-profile.cjs` and `scan-integration.cjs`, scores structural, ruleCoherence, integration, outputQuality, and systemFitness dimensions, applies weights and promotion gates, caches by input hash, and emits a `scored` result with `mode: 'agent-improvement'`. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:83:| `trade-off-detector.cjs` | Library exports (`detectTradeOffs`, `getTrajectory`, `checkParetoDominance`) flagging cross-dimension regressions using hard and soft dimension thresholds. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:84:| `benchmark-stability.cjs` | Library exports (`measureStability`, `stabilityCoefficient`, `generateWeightRecommendations`, and related) reporting score variance and weight-optimization advisories. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:85:| `check-mirror-drift.cjs` | CLI reporting drift between a canonical agent body and its mirrors. Args include `--output`, `--canonical`, `--mirrors`, `--manifest`. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:94:| Imports | May import `../lib/*` (`typed-errors.cjs`, `promotion-gates.cjs`). `score-candidate.cjs` spawns sibling `generate-profile.cjs` and `scan-integration.cjs` as child processes. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/agent-improvement/README.md:95:| Exports | `candidate-lineage.cjs`, `trade-off-detector.cjs`, and `benchmark-stability.cjs` expose named module exports. `score-candidate.cjs`, `generate-profile.cjs`, `scan-integration.cjs`, `check-mirror-drift.cjs`, and `rollback-candidate.cjs` run `main()` as CLI entrypoints. |
