.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/lib/README.md:16:`lib/` holds the scorer-internal cache. `cache.cjs` provides an atomic, append-only store for two cache kinds: `det` for deterministic check results and `grader` for grader-call results. The grader harness uses it to skip repeat dispatches for an identical input bundle.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/lib/README.md:20:- Blobs are written with a temp-file-then-rename for atomicity and indexed in an append-only `index.jsonl` per kind.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/lib/README.md:23:- The on-disk `cache/` directory under the scorer is git-ignored runtime state.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/lib/README.md:31:| `cache.cjs` | Exports `derive_det_key`, `derive_grader_key`, `write_atomic`, `read`, `cache_hit`, `read_index`, `rebuild_index`, plus the `PACKET_ROOT`, `CACHE_ROOT`, and lock-TTL constants. Stores blobs under `cache/<kind>/<key>.out.md` with a `cache-meta` header and indexes them in `cache/<kind>/index.jsonl`. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/lib/README.md:40:| Consumers | Required by `../grader/harness.cjs`. The cache is internal to the scorer and is not a cross-skill import surface. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/lib/README.md:41:| Storage root | `CACHE_ROOT` resolves to `cache/` one level above this file, under the scorer. That directory is git-ignored runtime state. |
