.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/README.md:16:`scorer/` owns the 5-dimension scoring engine for Lane B. `score-model-variant.cjs` takes primitive criteria plus an absolute `cwd`, runs the deterministic check subprocesses and the grader, and returns a weighted score with the per-dimension breakdown.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/README.md:20:- The public `score()` API takes criteria and an absolute `cwd`, never a fixture file path. The caller passes the criteria as data.
