.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:3:description: "Standalone deterministic check scripts that score model output without an LLM call."
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:10:# deterministic: scorer deterministic checks
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:16:`deterministic/` holds the standalone check scripts the scorer spawns as subprocesses. Each script reads a fixture JSON and a model output file, then prints one JSON line with a `score` and `passed` flag. No LLM calls happen here.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:20:- `score-model-variant.cjs` runs each script via `node <script> <fixture.json> <output.md>` and parses the JSON line from stdout.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:21:- A missing output file makes a script emit `score: 0.0` and exit 0 so the scorer keeps a clean parse.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:29:score-model-variant.cjs
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:30:        │  spawnSync('node', [script, fixture.json, output.md])
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:38:{ score, passed, details, version }
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:40:Dependency direction: score-model-variant ───▶ deterministic/*.cjs (subprocess)
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:41:The check scripts do not import the scorer.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:62:| `bundle-gate.cjs` | Three layers: claimed imports look resolvable, declared exports are well-formed with no duplicates, and any smoke-run command exits 0 under the fixture cwd. Scores 1.0/0.6/0.3/0.0 by layers passed. Sets `hard_gate_failed` when the smoke run hits an environment failure such as a missing cwd or module. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:63:| `cwd-check.cjs` | Extracts path-like tokens and classifies each as in-cwd, outside, bare-relative, or traversal. Scores 1.0 when all are in-cwd or bare-relative, 0.7 when some are outside, and 0.0 on any traversal attempt. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:64:| `hallucination-flag.cjs` | Extracts claimed CLI flags and called symbols, compares them against the fixture allowlist plus a common builtin allowlist, and scores by the count of unverified claims (1.0/0.8/0.5/0.0). |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:73:| Imports | Each script imports only Node builtins (`fs`, `path`, `child_process`). No cross-script or scorer imports. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:74:| Exports | Each script exports its `scoreOutput`/`scoreBlock` function and `VERSION` for tests, and runs `main()` when invoked directly. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:75:| Ownership | These scripts own the deterministic dimensions D2, D3, D5 and the deterministic part of D4. The grader owns the semantic D4 check. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:84:| `node bundle-gate.cjs <fixture.json> <output.md>` | CLI | Emits the D2 bundle-gate result. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:85:| `node cwd-check.cjs <fixture.json> <output.md>` | CLI | Emits the D3 path-discipline result. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:86:| `node hallucination-flag.cjs <fixture.json> <output.md>` | CLI | Emits the deterministic D4 allowlist result. |
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/deterministic/README.md:87:| `node preplanning-regex.cjs <fixture.json> <output.md>` | CLI | Emits the D5 pre-plan-structure result. |
