.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/grader/prompts/system-grader.md:7:Read the fixture metadata and the SWE 1.6 output. Score the output on the named dimension. Return JSON ONLY (no preamble, no markdown, no explanation outside the JSON object).
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/grader/prompts/system-grader.md:11:```json
