.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/grader/prompts/system-grader.md:24:Score 1.0 if every CLI flag, function/symbol name, and file path referenced in the output is either:
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/grader/prompts/system-grader.md:25:- In the fixture's allowlist.cli_flags, allowlist.symbols, OR
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/model-benchmark/scorer/grader/prompts/system-grader.md:30:- Invented CLI flags (e.g., --reasoning-effort when fixture says it doesn't exist)
